      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="g2" style="margin-top:14px">
      <div class="card card-t">
        <div class="sec-label">2050 With-Action Scenario</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:var(--teal)">${last.withLST}°C</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mut)">Projected mean LST by 2050 with full intervention programme, versus ${last.bauLST}°C under BAU — a <b style="color:var(--teal)">${r1(last.bauLST-last.withLST)}°C improvement</b>.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-r">
        <div class="sec-label">2050 Business As Usual</div>
